org.apache.flink.cep.nfa

类 NFA<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.cep.nfa.NFA<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Type of the processed events
    所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable

    public class NFA<T>
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Non-deterministic finite automaton implementation.

    The NFA processes input events which will chnage the internal state machine. Whenever a final state is reached, the matching sequence of events is emitted. The implementation is strongly based on the paper "Efficient Pattern Matching over Event Streams".

    另请参阅:
    https://people.cs.umass.edu/~yanlei/publications/sase-sigmod08.pdf, 序列化表格

      • process

        public org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<Collection<Map<String,T>>,Collection<org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<Map<String,T>,Long>>> process(T event,
                                                                                                                                                        long timestamp)
        Processes the next input event. If some of the computations reach a final state then the resulting event sequences are returned. If computations time out and timeout handling is activated, then the timed out event patterns are returned.
        参数:
        event - The current event to be processed or null if only pruning shall be done
        timestamp - The timestamp of the current event
        返回:
        Tuple of the collection of matched patterns (e.g. the result of computations which have reached a final state) and the collection of timed out patterns (if timeout handling is activated)
